Package: sda-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: SN360 Desktop Agent Contributors <security@example.com>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), adduser
Recommends: systemd
Homepage: https://github.com/kennguy3n/sn360-desktop-agent
Description: Lightweight Wazuh-compatible security agent for desktops and laptops.
 SN360 Desktop Agent (SDA) is a modular, cross-platform security agent
 written in Rust. It provides file integrity monitoring, log collection,
 system inventory, security configuration assessment, rootkit detection,
 and active response, all optimized for sub-15 MB RAM and near-invisible
 CPU impact on end-user devices.
